title: Full Combine Recap + Jordan Love & More Prospect Interviews
itunes:title: Full Combine Recap + Jordan Love & More Prospect Interviews
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode after coming back from the 2020 NFL Scouting Combine. To start off, the guys talk about the top performers at the combine (1:38). After that, they give big picture combine takeaways (26:42). Next, the duo give their QB takeaways from the combine (36:45). Then, Bucky interviews Utah State QB Jordan Love (45:36), Washington QB Jacob Eason (49:01) and LSU WR Justin Jefferson (55:17).
